title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1995-03-19
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway, Walkin' Blues, So Many Roads, Easy Answers, Don't Ease Me In, Unbroken Chain

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Way To Go Home, Crazy Fingers, Corinna-> Mathilda-> Drums-> Space-> I Need A Miracle-> Stella Blue-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

First Unbroken Chain

reviews.review_text: What a Stella Blue!! I've never heard him get that ,beautiful tone out of the Lightning Bolt,I'll bet he's playing the Rosebud!It just doen't have that piezo tone?
